summary: My current and long time preset for Racemenu
descriptionHtml:
EDIT: I have discovered that i was using bodychange at the time of making the preset and for some people it is required for the preset to load correctly

This is my preset for my player character Axena. Its my first upload so I hope you guys like her. If you wanna get some more reference check images

Don't download with NMM. Download manually and put file in Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

Required mods to look the same as in screenshots:
SG Hair: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5ovhttJqGRWZUZsODlENTk1bGs/edit
True Eyes: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?
Freckle Mania: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?
UNPCM Body: http://mod.dysintropi.me/unpcm/

I will do my best to answer any questions left in the comments 

Thank to the creators of the mods above for making mods that led to me making this cutie
author: Lyrinthia
